graph TB
    subgraph "AI Gateway Payload Processing Service"
        direction TB
        BBR["BBR Runtime<br/>(ext_proc gRPC Server)<br/>Port 9004/TCP"]
        Health["Health Check<br/>Port 9005/TCP"]

        subgraph "Plugin Chain (ordered)"
            direction TB
            P1["body-field-to-header<br/>(upstream built-in)<br/>Extracts model field → X-Gateway-Model-Name header"]
            P2["model-provider-resolver<br/>(RequestProcessor)<br/>Resolves model → provider, targetModel, credentialRef"]
            P3["api-translation<br/>(Request + ResponseProcessor)<br/>Translates OpenAI ↔ provider-native formats"]
            P4["apikey-injection<br/>(RequestProcessor)<br/>Injects provider-specific auth headers"]
            P5["nemo-request-guard<br/>(RequestProcessor, optional)<br/>Enforces NeMo content safety rails"]
            P1 --> P2 --> P3 --> P4 --> P5
        end

        BBR -->|executes| P1
    end

    subgraph "CycleState (inter-plugin data)"
        CS["provider | model | credential-ref-name | credential-ref-namespace"]
    end

    P2 -->|writes| CS
    P3 -->|reads| CS
    P4 -->|reads| CS

    Client["Client<br/>(OpenAI Chat Completions API)"] -->|POST /v1/chat/completions| Envoy
    Envoy["Envoy Gateway<br/>(Istio)"] -->|ext_proc gRPC<br/>9004/TCP| BBR
    BBR -->|mutated request/response| Envoy

    ExternalModelCR["ExternalModel CR<br/>(maas.opendatahub.io/v1alpha1)"]
    ExternalModelCR -->|watched by<br/>controller-runtime| P2

    SecretsCR["Kubernetes Secrets<br/>(labeled bbr-managed=true)"]
    SecretsCR -->|watched by<br/>controller-runtime| P4

    NeMo["NeMo Guardrails Service"]
    P5 -->|POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP| NeMo

    subgraph "Provider Translators"
        direction LR
        T1["OpenAI<br/>(pass-through)"]
        T2["Anthropic<br/>(full body translation)"]
        T3["Azure OpenAI<br/>(path rewrite + field strip)"]
        T4["Vertex AI OpenAI<br/>(path rewrite)"]
        T5["AWS Bedrock<br/>(path rewrite)"]
    end

    P3 -->|delegates to| T1
    P3 -->|delegates to| T2
    P3 -->|delegates to| T3
    P3 -->|delegates to| T4
    P3 -->|delegates to| T5

    Envoy -->|HTTPS/443| Providers["External AI Providers<br/>(OpenAI, Anthropic, Azure, Vertex, Bedrock)"]

    style BBR fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Health fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style P1 fill:#6baed6,stroke:#333
    style P2 fill:#6baed6,stroke:#333
    style P3 fill:#6baed6,stroke:#333
    style P4 fill:#6baed6,stroke:#333
    style P5 fill:#6baed6,stroke:#333
    style CS fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#d6b656
    style ExternalModelCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style SecretsCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style Envoy fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style NeMo fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Client fill:#f9f9f9,stroke:#999
    style Providers fill:#f9f9f9,stroke:#999
    style T1 fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#82b366
    style T2 fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#82b366
    style T3 fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#82b366
    style T4 fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#82b366
    style T5 fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#82b366
